quran[15{c,v,t}:
72,14,aur yeh ke hum mein baaz farmanbardar hain aur baaz ( nafarman ) gunehgaar hain. to jo farmanbardar hue woh seedhay raste par chalay
72,15,aur jo gunehgaar hue woh dozakh ka eendhan banay
72,16,aur ( ae paighambar ) yeh ( bhi un se keh do ) ke agar yeh log seedhay raste par rehtay to hum un ke peenay ko bohat sa pani dete
72,17,taakay is se un ki azmaish karen. aur jo shakhs apne perwar-digaar ki yaad se munh phairay ga woh is ko sakht azaab mein daakhil kere ga
72,18,aur yeh ke msjdin ( khaas ) khuda ki hain to khuda ke sath kisi aur ki ibadat nah karo
72,19,aur jab khuda ke bande ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) is ki ibadat ko kharray hue to kafir un ke gird hajhoom kar lanay ko they
72,20,keh do ke mein to apne perwar-digaar hi ki ibadat karta hon aur kisi ko is ka shareek nahi banata
72,21,( yeh bhi ) keh do ke mein tumahray haq mein nuqsaan aur naffa ka kuch ikhtiyar nahi rakhta
72,22,( yeh bhi ) keh do ke khuda ( ke azaab ) se mujhe koi panah nahi day sakta. aur mein is ke siwa kahin jaye panah nahi daikhta
72,23,haan khuda ki taraf se ehkaam ka aur is ke pighamon ka pouncha dena ( hi ) mere zimmay hai. aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke paighambar ki nafarmani kere ga to aison ke liye jahannum ki aag hai hamesha hamesha is mein rahen ge
72,24,yahan taq ke jab yeh log woh ( din ) dekh len ge jis ka un se wadakiya jata hai tab un ko maloom ho jaye ga ke madadgaar kis ke kamzor aur shumaar kin ka thora hai
72,25,keh do ke jis ( din ) ka tum se wadakiya jata hai mein nahi jaanta ke woh ( an ) qareeb ( anay wala hai ) ya mere perwar-digaar ne is ki muddat daraaz kar di hai
72,26,ghaib ( ki baat ) jan-nay wala hai aur kisi par apne ghaib ko zahir nahi karta
72,27,haan jis paighambar ko pasand farmaiye to is ( ko ghaib ki baatein bta deta aur is ) ke agay aur peechay nigehbaan muqarrar kar deta hai
72,28,taakay maloom farmaiye ke unhon ne apne perwar-digaar ke pegham pouncha diye hain aur ( yun to ) is ne un ki sab cheezon ko har taraf se qaboo kar rakha hai aur aik aik cheez gun rakhi hai
